Package net.proteusframework.processes.form.registration Description

Spring registration for form fields. For a field to be available in the FormEditor, it must have a FormElementRegistration available to Spring. These are exposed through one of the FormElementRegistrationFactory implementations. FormElementRegistrations can be autowired to the FormElementRegistrationFactoryImpl by making use of the FormElementRegistrationConfiguration.
